				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "There are many software implementations of the Sakoda-Schelling model today. Because Schelling did not aim for unambiguous rules, they all behave somewhat differently. Those differences are mostly undocumented, except by the source code of the software."
			},
