				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "You can play with such a traditional implementation on the page [[A Pharo implementation of the Sakoda-Schelling model]]. Please go ahead and run it a few times. It gives a better intuition for how these simulations work. If you know some Smalltalk, you should also read the code overview given on that page. The additional assumptions in the code, compared to the paper, are much better explained than for most other implementations."
